Features

- Add your projects/portfolio in the sidebar.
- Generate multiple cold emails for a given job description.
- Light/Dark theme toggle.
- Adjustable number of emails and top portfolio items.
- Download generated emails as **PDF** or **TXT**.
- Tabs UI to view multiple generated emails easily.
- Compact, easy-to-read code structure.

Requirements

Streamlit
langchain
grok
fpdf
io
Openai embeddings
Chromadb
